jointly to Nuada,

713
01:03:32,558 --> 01:03:34,726
our most sacred god of the sun,

714
01:03:34,852 --> 01:03:38,355
and to Avellenau,
the beloved goddess of our orchards,

715
01:03:38,481 --> 01:03:42,734
in order that we may furnish them
with renewed power

716
01:03:42,860 --> 01:03:45,362
