720
01:04:01,128 --> 01:04:05,215
Mrs Morrison, I don't know
if you know it or not,

721
01:04:05,341 --> 01:04:08,301
but Rowan is not dead,
they've got her hidden somewhere.

722
01:04:08,427 --> 01:04:09,928
They?

723
01:04:10,054 --> 01:04:13,849
